Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去碰頭的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  下一個該選誰好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去聽一下奏的意見好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音無同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直井！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.82,0:02:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是從哪裡冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你們倆找我有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs20\pos(630,350)}哦對了  這是想去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs20\pos(420,350)}哦是了  你這是想去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs20\pos(610,350)}音無同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs20\pos(380,350)}音無
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關你什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找音無有事  為了能幫上他的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是個礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快給我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  看著我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是廁所裡的捲紙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去發現廁紙被一瞬間沖走時的爽快感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我幫你的忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底知不知道我要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想讓所有人一個接一個地消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話由你說出來就像要去犯罪似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  直井
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該已經沒什麼留戀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你在一起  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想比這傢伙先消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因為這種理由而留在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒在問你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  音無同學  你不是需要同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就請盡情地使用我好了  音無同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  又幹了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.63,0:03:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人嗎  我可以開槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有東西跑進來了  音無同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西打不死的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向同學  音無同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人對敵  打敗敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二個也出現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說很有可能是天使的新技能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但感覺不太對勁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知戰線全體成員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後禁止單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也要兩人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把影子視為不同於天使的另一敵對勢力處置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那游離子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游離子要去排除其他所能想到的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.12,up,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長的立華奏同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.75,up,NTP,0,0,0,,請立即到學生會辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  這不是游離子的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.27,up,NTP,0,0,0,,重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  我們想幹的事情搞不好穿幫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.58,up,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長的立華奏同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.07,up,NTP,0,0,0,,請立即到學生會辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我們也旁聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是身為原學生會長代理  現副會長的我許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡是學生會辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  到底是怎麼回事  那個影子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你編寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就有可能是BUG了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近一次編程是在什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間上來說是完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要進你的房間檢查  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹山君  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解  還有請叫我Kleist…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你編的是什麼樣的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翅膀？  長翅膀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說想要飛起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  裝飾？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有人說那樣看起來更像天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人說…  誰說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓學生會長如虎添翼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是身為原學生會長代理  現副會長的我提議的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長長翅膀後就能如虎添翼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長加  翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  居然這麼溫順呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點兒都沒有冷酷的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來和以前沒什麼不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  已經十分冷酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副會長的我每天都被她刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長心情不好的時候接近她就會被刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為副會長的我在她身邊的時候很多  所以經常被刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也被刺得腸肚外露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過她現在似乎心情不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽得見嗎  請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是竹山君嗎  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.20,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}女生宿舍  天使領域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發現BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這次的程式只是簡單的裝飾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會產生帶有意識會襲擊人的BUG
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有請稱呼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的程式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被動技能有「overdrive」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主動技能有「handsonic」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以前的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但形狀不一樣了  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算刪掉嗎  那樣的話又要從頭開始做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  有聽到槍聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼  哪來的槍聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是外面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然會有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游離子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音無同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音無君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dancing  in  the  shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I  kiss  you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想被那東西刺到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙  想把同伴也一起砍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自有分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別算這麼精確啊  很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別犯傻了  注意掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼呀  怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種毛骨悚然的東西是從未在這個世界出現過的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是噩夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿誘惑的嘉年華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是我們在這個世界待太久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲裡不是常有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止玩家一直玩下去而出現的無敵怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真笑不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是夥伴一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤卷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  高松他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高松他被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:26.89,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教學樓  走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被那個影子吃掉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吃掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到他的時候  他全身都被影子包裹著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後連眼鏡都掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他居然會被弄掉眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被地面吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事  有一股別的勢力開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到高松了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在擔心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心？  擔心什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被那影子怪吃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己完全沒有注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被影子吃掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後被地面吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時一樣從宿舍裡起床
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就來上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來上學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你換成那套制服來上課了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會消失的啊  你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失？  什麼會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  這傢伙變得奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然本來就是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高松…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  日向君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你打擾到我上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎  放著他不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會消失的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大山君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.80,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}教學樓  A棟  樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的那些問答就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成NPC了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不明所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NPC的話就是沒有靈魂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他的靈魂到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被那東西給吃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道他連消失也不能  必須永遠在這裡上課了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣比死還慘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠…永遠都要被囚禁在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界居然會發生這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不如被天使消滅更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且影子似乎還在不斷增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  該怎麼辦啊  游離子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界發生了異變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了天使之外的新敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點直接  姑且稱其為影子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和天使不同  影子神出鬼沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無差別地在進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被影子吃掉的人會失去靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成每天都會去上課的NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在影子正在無限制增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且原因不明  目前也毫無對策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以和之前游佐所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠集體行動來防衛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  在這危機關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個死後世界戰線之中出現了抱有另一種看法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們正將戰線引向新的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那條道路也許會是迴避目前危機的一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  作為他們的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音無君  能請你在此和大家說清楚你的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿幫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑  別說得那麼輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有那麼合適的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  那種事不可能出現在這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由依找到了那條路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連我這樣死前是個人渣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能在這個世界給別人指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說我是神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有音無同學替我取回了人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一句認可我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要選擇哪一條道路由大家自己去判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游離子呢  游離子你要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來都是很亂來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不會保護你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在做我想做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自去考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她去對付影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起開動腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她更適合去直接戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是瞞不過游離子的眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但奏是我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的成員也是你們的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保護他們就需要她的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能與我們戰線抗衡到現在的那壓倒性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實這差事很適合天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她並不是天使哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們一樣是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒發覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神早就看穿了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也在動搖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我不是什麼天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見面時我就是這麼回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說你是天使什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是什麼天使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的說過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生過很多事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你們的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼奏為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為學生會長的她  為什麼沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她有要留在這裡的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼她和我們一樣  也背負著什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要把那個解開才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些事情想去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去和影子戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:17:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟我給了其他人選擇的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也應該有人會跟著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要時間考慮的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這樣說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大家都消失了  平安地離開了這個世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會認為這都是你的功勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人等著的話會被影子幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在被幹掉之前你也快點離開這個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  會在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然之間在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我們倆開創的戰線嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起走過了很長一段時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以結束的時候也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會丟下你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是一樣的傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情用事解決不了任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵襲  敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小奏  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「handsonic  version5」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  還能再見面的話就到時候見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游離子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好過分的綽號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是說不定就是因為這個才被大家所仰慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就到此為止吧
