Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下棋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.08,0:22:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經是電腦時代了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.64,0:22:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩玩非數位化遊戲也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻有不錯的興趣愛好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在安裝新電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能因為電腦很值錢  總被偷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.55,0:22:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不夠了就得補充
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有發現犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前為止還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你叫住真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個盜竊犯現在正扮演著這世界的神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用著無數的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始介入NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎麼才能抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在影子也在不斷增加中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是偷  但這也不是能輕易就搬走的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘著夜色潛入  把電腦裝車  帶到外面去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說從窗戶？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等等  難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是Guild啊
